text: Dornum is a village and a municipality in Aurich, in Lower Saxony, Germany. It is near the North Sea coast, about 15 km east of Norden, and 20 km north of Aurich. ==Division of the municipality== The other towns in the municipality of Dornum are: Ne√ümersiel, Dornumersiel, Nesse, Roggenstede, Westerbur, Westeraccum, Schwittersum. ==References== ==Other websites== * www.dornum.de * Pipe organ concert tour Category:Towns and villages in East Frisia Category:Aurich (district)
